    <div id="site-intro">
<div id="site-intro-container"><span class="intro-swril swril-left"> </span><span class="intro-text">Taking care of your schedules. Scheduling people with care.</span><span class="intro-swril swril-right"> </span></div>
</div>
<p>Schedule Care is an easy to use software system for nursing homes. Imagine losing those scheduling headaches while gaining time so that you can do what&#8217;s important to you.</p>
<blockquote><p>I can spend time doing more meaningful things!<br />
Christine</p></blockquote>
<p>With ScheduleCare, you&#8217;ll find scheduling staff a whole lot easier. You&#8217;ll be less stressed because our system does the hard work for you. We&#8217;ve automated most of those tasks that take your time and give you a headache. There&#8217;s over ten years of thoughtful design into the software, thinking of how to create an accurate and easy to use system. It&#8217;s easy. It&#8217;s powerful. It&#8217;s automated. And it&#8217;s reasonably priced.</p>
<p>You&#8217;ll also have improved budgeting because of accurate tracking of staff hours and categories. That&#8217;s in addition to less errors and less overtime costs.</p>
<p>Best of all, ScheduleCare frees up your time so that you and your staff can concentrate on more important business goals.</p>
<p>Our clients, long term care facilities throughout Eastern and Maritime Canada, have found ScheduleCare both easy and effective. Find out why they love ScheduleCare.  <strong><a title="Contact" href="/?page_id=8">Contact us</a></strong> for a no obligation consultation.</p>
   

